{"pageid":340786,"pagename":"Fragment Hunt","title":"Fragment Hunt","displaytitle":"Fragment Hunt","revid":14219895,"properties":[{"name":"smw-semanticdata-status","value":""},{"name":"page_image_free","value":"Clue_scroll_detail.png"},{"name":"description","value":"Fragment Hunt is a special event with clues being on the Old School RuneScape Twitter in December 2021, with each clue eventually leading to a name of a Fragment in the upcoming Shattered Relics League."}],"content":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"floatright\"><a href=\"/w/File:Clue_scroll_detail.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Clue scroll detail.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/Clue_scroll_detail.png/130px-Clue_scroll_detail.png?ef179\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"130\" height=\"114\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/Clue_scroll_detail.png/195px-Clue_scroll_detail.png?ef179 1.5x, /images/thumb/Clue_scroll_detail.png/260px-Clue_scroll_detail.png?ef179 2x\" data-file-width=\"756\" data-file-height=\"661\" /></a></div>\n<p><b>Fragment Hunt</b> is a special event with clues being on the <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://twitter.com/OldSchoolRS\">Old School RuneScape Twitter</a> in December <a href=\"/w/2021\" title=\"2021\">2021</a>, with each clue eventually leading to a name of a <a href=\"/w/Shattered_Relics_League#Fragments\" title=\"Shattered Relics League\">Fragment</a> in the upcoming <a href=\"/w/Shattered_Relics_League\" title=\"Shattered Relics League\">Shattered Relics League</a>.\n</p><p>The first person to <code><a href=\"/w/Mod_Sarnie\" title=\"Mod Sarnie\">@JagexSarnie</a></code> on Twitter, with <code>#FragmentHunt</code> and solve the name wins 6 months of <a href=\"/w/Membership\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Membership\">Membership</a>. This was confirmed solved by Jagex in their day 5 tweet on 22 December 2021, at 12:00 PM.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\" role=\"navigation\" aria-labelledby=\"mw-toc-heading\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en-GB\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2 id=\"mw-toc-heading\">Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Day_1\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Day 1</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Day_2\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Day 2</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Day_3\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Day 3</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Day_4\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Day 4</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Day_5\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Day 5</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#The_fragment\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">The fragment</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#Teaser\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">7</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Teaser</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Day_1\">Day 1</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Fragment_Hunt?section=1&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Day 1\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Fragment_Hunt?action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Day 1\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The first tweet and clue were released on <a href=\"/w/18_December\" title=\"18 December\">18 December</a> <a href=\"/w/2021\" title=\"2021\">2021</a>:\n</p>\n<table align=\"center\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse; border-style:none; background-color:transparent;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<td class=\"quotation-mark\" style=\"width:20px; vertical-align:top; font-size:40px; font-family:serif; font-weight:bold; text-align:left; padding:10px 10px;\">“\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top; padding:4px 10px;\">Fragments have started to reveal themselves...\n<p>Over the next few days, dIscover a trail of clues across our newsposts to uncover a new Fragment.\n</p><p>Good Luck! The first person to @JagexSarnie on Twitter with #FragmentHunt &amp; solve the name will win 6 months of Membership.\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"quotation-mark\" style=\"width:20px; vertical-align:bottom; font-size:40px; font-family:serif; font-weight:bold; text-align:right; padding:10px 10px;\">”\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&#160;\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top\">\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<div class=\"center\"><div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/w/File:Fragment_Hunt_-_Day_1_clue.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Fragment Hunt - Day 1 clue.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/Fragment_Hunt_-_Day_1_clue.jpg/400px-Fragment_Hunt_-_Day_1_clue.jpg?bc845\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"400\" height=\"200\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/Fragment_Hunt_-_Day_1_clue.jpg/600px-Fragment_Hunt_-_Day_1_clue.jpg?bc845 1.5x, /images/thumb/Fragment_Hunt_-_Day_1_clue.jpg/800px-Fragment_Hunt_-_Day_1_clue.jpg?bc845 2x\" data-file-width=\"1757\" data-file-height=\"878\" /></a></div></div>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<table class=\"mw-collapsible mw-collapsed\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>Click \"Expand\" to view solution\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<div class=\"center\"><div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/w/Special:Upload?wpDestFile=Fragment_Hunt_-_Day_1_solution.png\" class=\"new\" title=\"File:Fragment Hunt - Day 1 solution.png\">File:Fragment Hunt - Day 1 solution.png</a></div></div>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Day_2\">Day 2</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Fragment_Hunt?section=2&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Day 2\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Fragment_Hunt?action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Day 2\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The second clue was released on <a href=\"/w/19_December\" title=\"19 December\">19 December</a> <a href=\"/w/2021\" title=\"2021\">2021</a>:\n</p>\n<table align=\"center\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse; border-style:none; background-color:transparent;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<td class=\"quotation-mark\" style=\"width:20px; vertical-align:top; font-size:40px; font-family:serif; font-weight:bold; text-align:left; padding:10px 10px;\">“\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top; padding:4px 10px;\">Another clue uncovered...\n<p>Will you be the firSt to solve all of the puzzles?\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"quotation-mark\" style=\"width:20px; vertical-align:bottom; font-size:40px; font-family:serif; font-weight:bold; text-align:right; padding:10px 10px;\">”\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&#160;\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top\">\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<div class=\"center\"><div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/w/File:Fragment_Hunt_-_Day_2_clue.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Fragment Hunt - Day 2 clue.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/Fragment_Hunt_-_Day_2_clue.jpg/400px-Fragment_Hunt_-_Day_2_clue.jpg?2a973\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"400\" height=\"200\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/Fragment_Hunt_-_Day_2_clue.jpg/600px-Fragment_Hunt_-_Day_2_clue.jpg?2a973 1.5x, /images/thumb/Fragment_Hunt_-_Day_2_clue.jpg/800px-Fragment_Hunt_-_Day_2_clue.jpg?2a973 2x\" data-file-width=\"1757\" data-file-height=\"878\" /></a></div></div>\n<table class=\"mw-collapsible mw-collapsed\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>Click \"Expand\" to view solution\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<div class=\"center\"><div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/w/Special:Upload?wpDestFile=Fragment_Hunt_-_Day_2_solution.png\" class=\"new\" title=\"File:Fragment Hunt - Day 2 solution.png\">File:Fragment Hunt - Day 2 solution.png</a></div></div>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Day_3\">Day 3</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Fragment_Hunt?section=3&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Day 3\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Fragment_Hunt?action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Day 3\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The third clue was released on <a href=\"/w/20_December\" title=\"20 December\">20 December</a> <a href=\"/w/2021\" title=\"2021\">2021</a>:\n</p>\n<table align=\"center\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse; border-style:none; background-color:transparent;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<td class=\"quotation-mark\" style=\"width:20px; vertical-align:top; font-size:40px; font-family:serif; font-weight:bold; text-align:left; padding:10px 10px;\">“\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top; padding:4px 10px;\">This marks the halfway point.\n<p>We've been enjoying alL the theories and guesses so far, but who will be the first?\n</p><p>Don't forget to @JagexSarnie on Twitter with #FragmentHunt and the answer to win 6 months of membership!\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"quotation-mark\" style=\"width:20px; vertical-align:bottom; font-size:40px; font-family:serif; font-weight:bold; text-align:right; padding:10px 10px;\">”\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&#160;\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top\">\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<div class=\"center\"><div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/w/File:Fragment_Hunt_-_Day_3_clue.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Fragment Hunt - Day 3 clue.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/Fragment_Hunt_-_Day_3_clue.jpg/400px-Fragment_Hunt_-_Day_3_clue.jpg?423d3\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"400\" height=\"200\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/Fragment_Hunt_-_Day_3_clue.jpg/600px-Fragment_Hunt_-_Day_3_clue.jpg?423d3 1.5x, /images/thumb/Fragment_Hunt_-_Day_3_clue.jpg/800px-Fragment_Hunt_-_Day_3_clue.jpg?423d3 2x\" data-file-width=\"1757\" data-file-height=\"878\" /></a></div></div>\n<table class=\"mw-collapsible mw-collapsed\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>Click \"Expand\" to view solution\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<div class=\"center\"><div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/w/Special:Upload?wpDestFile=Fragment_Hunt_-_Day_3_solution.png\" class=\"new\" title=\"File:Fragment Hunt - Day 3 solution.png\">File:Fragment Hunt - Day 3 solution.png</a></div></div>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Day_4\">Day 4</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Fragment_Hunt?section=4&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Day 4\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Fragment_Hunt?action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Day 4\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The fourth clue was released on <a href=\"/w/21_December\" title=\"21 December\">21 December</a> <a href=\"/w/2021\" title=\"2021\">2021</a>:\n</p>\n<table align=\"center\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse; border-style:none; background-color:transparent;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<td class=\"quotation-mark\" style=\"width:20px; vertical-align:top; font-size:40px; font-family:serif; font-weight:bold; text-align:left; padding:10px 10px;\">“\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top; padding:4px 10px;\">Another secret lies hidden amongst the completed solution.\n<p>Can you discover where the secret frAgment is kept?\n</p>\n<ol><li>FragmentHunt</li></ol>\n</td>\n<td class=\"quotation-mark\" style=\"width:20px; vertical-align:bottom; font-size:40px; font-family:serif; font-weight:bold; text-align:right; padding:10px 10px;\">”\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&#160;\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top\">\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<div class=\"center\"><div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/w/File:Fragment_Hunt_-_Day_4_clue.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Fragment Hunt - Day 4 clue.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/Fragment_Hunt_-_Day_4_clue.jpg/400px-Fragment_Hunt_-_Day_4_clue.jpg?cf922\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"400\" height=\"200\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/Fragment_Hunt_-_Day_4_clue.jpg/600px-Fragment_Hunt_-_Day_4_clue.jpg?cf922 1.5x, /images/thumb/Fragment_Hunt_-_Day_4_clue.jpg/800px-Fragment_Hunt_-_Day_4_clue.jpg?cf922 2x\" data-file-width=\"1757\" data-file-height=\"878\" /></a></div></div>\n<table class=\"mw-collapsible mw-collapsed\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>Click \"Expand\" to view solution\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<div class=\"center\"><div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/w/Special:Upload?wpDestFile=Fragment_Hunt_-_Day_4_solution.png\" class=\"new\" title=\"File:Fragment Hunt - Day 4 solution.png\">File:Fragment Hunt - Day 4 solution.png</a></div></div>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Day_5\">Day 5</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Fragment_Hunt?section=5&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Day 5\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Fragment_Hunt?action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Day 5\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The fifth clue was released on <a href=\"/w/22_December\" title=\"22 December\">22 December</a> <a href=\"/w/2021\" title=\"2021\">2021</a>:\n</p>\n<table align=\"center\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse; border-style:none; background-color:transparent;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<td class=\"quotation-mark\" style=\"width:20px; vertical-align:top; font-size:40px; font-family:serif; font-weight:bold; text-align:left; padding:10px 10px;\">“\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top; padding:4px 10px;\">Someone has solved the puzzle!\n<p>Here's the fiNal trail of clues to finish off the #Fragmenthunt.\n</p><p>Stay tuneD for more details on the fragment which we'll reveal tomorrow.\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"quotation-mark\" style=\"width:20px; vertical-align:bottom; font-size:40px; font-family:serif; font-weight:bold; text-align:right; padding:10px 10px;\">”\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&#160;\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top\">\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<div class=\"center\"><div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/w/File:Fragment_Hunt_-_Day_5_clue.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Fragment Hunt - Day 5 clue.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/Fragment_Hunt_-_Day_5_clue.jpg/400px-Fragment_Hunt_-_Day_5_clue.jpg?d994b\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"400\" height=\"200\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/Fragment_Hunt_-_Day_5_clue.jpg/600px-Fragment_Hunt_-_Day_5_clue.jpg?d994b 1.5x, /images/thumb/Fragment_Hunt_-_Day_5_clue.jpg/800px-Fragment_Hunt_-_Day_5_clue.jpg?d994b 2x\" data-file-width=\"1757\" data-file-height=\"878\" /></a></div></div>\n<table class=\"mw-collapsible mw-collapsed\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>Click \"Expand\" to view solution\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<div class=\"center\"><div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/w/Special:Upload?wpDestFile=Fragment_Hunt_-_Day_5_solution.png\" class=\"new\" title=\"File:Fragment Hunt - Day 5 solution.png\">File:Fragment Hunt - Day 5 solution.png</a></div></div>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"The_fragment\">The fragment</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Fragment_Hunt?section=6&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: The fragment\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Fragment_Hunt?action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: The fragment\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"mw-collapsible mw-collapsed\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>Click \"Expand\" to view the answer fragment's name\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Mother's Magic Fossils\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Teaser\">Teaser</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Fragment_Hunt?section=7&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Teaser\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Fragment_Hunt?action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: Teaser\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>On the <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://secure.runescape.com/m=news/fossil-island?oldschool=1\">Fossil Island update page</a>, there is a teaser to a fragment named <i>Golden Brick Road</i> discovered on <a href=\"/w/19_December\" title=\"19 December\">19 December</a> <a href=\"/w/2021\" title=\"2021\">2021</a>.\n</p>\n<div class=\"center\"><div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/w/File:Fragment_Hunt_-_Fragment_teaser.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Fragment Hunt - Fragment teaser.png\" src=\"/images/Fragment_Hunt_-_Fragment_teaser.png?1683e\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" data-file-width=\"32\" data-file-height=\"32\" /></a></div></div>\n<div class=\"center\"><div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/w/File:Fragment_Hunt_-_Golden_Brick_Road.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Fragment Hunt - Golden Brick Road.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/Fragment_Hunt_-_Golden_Brick_Road.png/400px-Fragment_Hunt_-_Golden_Brick_Road.png?50b7d\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"400\" height=\"225\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/Fragment_Hunt_-_Golden_Brick_Road.png/600px-Fragment_Hunt_-_Golden_Brick_Road.png?50b7d 1.5x, /images/thumb/Fragment_Hunt_-_Golden_Brick_Road.png/800px-Fragment_Hunt_-_Golden_Brick_Road.png?50b7d 2x\" data-file-width=\"1920\" data-file-height=\"1080\" /></a></div></div>\n<table class=\"navbox nowraplinks mw-collapsible\" data-expandtext=\"show\" data-navbox-name=\"Event