ount: 372/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 16948/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1003/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 5/100\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.010/10.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 767137/367001600 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   32.993      1 -total\n 87.12%   28.743      1 Template:Events\n 59.78%   19.722      1 Template:Navbox\n 19.90%    6.567      1 Template:Ctg\n 11.84%    3.906      5 Template:Cquote2\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key en_osrswiki:pcache:idhash:340786-0!canonical and timestamp 20220512003740 and revision id 14219895. Serialized with PHP.\n -->\n</div>","rawContent":"[[File:Clue scroll detail.png|right|130px]]\n'''Fragment Hunt''' is a special event with clues being on the [https://twitter.com/OldSchoolRS Old School RuneScape Twitter] in December [[2021]], with each clue eventually leading to a name of a [[Shattered Relics League#Fragments|Fragment]] in the upcoming [[Shattered Relics League]].\n\nThe first person to <code>[[Mod Sarnie|@JagexSarnie]]</code> on Twitter, with <code>#FragmentHunt</code> and solve the name wins 6 months of [[Membership]]. This was confirmed solved by Jagex in their day 5 tweet on 22 December 2021, at 12:00 PM.\n\n==Day 1==\nThe first tweet and clue were released on [[18 December]] [[2021]]:\n\n{{cquote2|Fragments have started to reveal themselves...\n\nOver the next few days, dIscover a trail of clues across our newsposts to uncover a new Fragment.\n\nGood Luck! The first person to @JagexSarnie on Twitter with #FragmentHunt & solve the name will win 6 months of Membership.||Old School RuneScape Twitter}}\n\n[[File:Fragment Hunt - Day 1 clue.jpg|centre|400px]]\n\n\n{| class=\"mw-collapsible mw-collapsed\"\n! Click \"Expand\" to view solution\n|-\n|\n[[File:Fragment Hunt - Day 1 solution.png|centre|400px]]\n|}\n\n==Day 2==\nThe second clue was released on [[19 December]] [[2021]]:\n\n{{cquote2|Another clue uncovered...\n\nWill you be the firSt to solve all of the puzzles?||Old School RuneScape Twitter}}\n\n[[File:Fragment Hunt - Day 2 clue.jpg|centre|400px]]\n\n{| class=\"mw-collapsible mw-collapsed\"\n! Click \"Expand\" to view solution\n|-\n|\n[[File:Fragment Hunt - Day 2 solution.png|centre|400px]]\n|}\n\n==Day 3==\nThe third clue was released on [[20 December]] [[2021]]:\n\n{{cquote2|This marks the halfway point.\n\nWe've been enjoying alL the theories and guesses so far, but who will be the first?\n\nDon't forget to @JagexSarnie on Twitter with #FragmentHunt and the answer to win 6 months of membership!||Old School RuneScape Twitter}}\n\n[[File:Fragment Hunt - Day 3 clue.jpg|centre|400px]]\n\n{| class=\"mw-collapsible mw-collapsed\"\n! Click \"Expand\" to view solution\n|-\n|\n[[File:Fragment Hunt - Day 3 solution.png|centre|400px]]\n|}\n\n==Day 4==\nThe fourth clue was released on [[21 December]] [[2021]]:\n\n{{cquote2|Another secret lies hidden amongst the completed solution.\n\nCan you discover where the secret frAgment is kept?\n\n#FragmentHunt||Old School RuneScape Twitter}}\n\n[[File:Fragment Hunt - Day 4 clue.jpg|centre|400px]]\n\n{| class=\"mw-collapsible mw-collapsed\"\n! Click \"Expand\" to view solution\n|-\n|\n[[File:Fragment Hunt - Day 4 solution.png|centre|400px]]\n|}\n\n==Day 5==\nThe fifth clue was released on [[22 December]] [[2021]]:\n\n{{cquote2|Someone has solved the puzzle!\n\nHere's the fiNal trail of clues to finish off the #Fragmenthunt.\n\nStay tuneD for more details on the fragment which we'll reveal tomorrow.||Old School RuneScape Twitter}}\n\n[[File:Fragment Hunt - Day 5 clue.jpg|centre|400px]]\n\n{| class=\"mw-collapsible mw-collapsed\"\n! Click \"Expand\" to view solution\n|-\n|\n[[File:Fragment Hunt - Day 5 solution.png|centre|400px]]\n|}\n\n==The fragment==\n{| class=\"mw-collapsible mw-collapsed\"\n! Click \"Expand\" to view the answer fragment's name\n|-\n|Mother's Magic Fossils\n|}\n\n==Teaser==\nOn the [https://secure.runescape.com/m=news/fossil-island?oldschool=1 Fossil Island update page], there is a teaser to a fragment named ''Golden Brick Road'' discovered on [[19 December]] [[2021]].\n\n[[File:Fragment Hunt - Fragment teaser.png|centre|32px]]\n[[File:Fragment Hunt - Golden Brick Road.png|centre|400px]]\n\n{{Events}}\n[[Category:Fragment Hunt]]"}